{"tid":868084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味係咪個個分完手先識得咩叫珍惜","createTime":"2018-10-19T07:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T19:34:53.000Z","uid":174992,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0699723b533df5f76d03f1d5674b04ebc6fdb9","tid":868084,"uid":174992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=to9fBWaaHGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dto9fBWaaHGI&d=Vm5jeO38HcOihhMeOd%2BulghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8c354154\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=to9fBWaaHGI</a><br />\n<br />\n「原來你這樣珍惜我<br />\n從前在熱戀中都未聽講過」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當初為你改呢樣為做個樣，你都覺得理所當然。<br />\n到叫分手先後悔，你先聽我講。<br />\n咁我之前咁辛苦係為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63780b356d21ec7ee38006f1f3af2268a31d51f","tid":868084,"uid":174992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f08e8db7e594612269ea591ed2eef66633837a5","tid":868084,"uid":87828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"因為發覺真係好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔住 你為我做咁多 我以前唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375ef924260a8b5f34ef708d89eedb04a4978836","tid":868084,"uid":174992,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1f08e8db7e594612269ea591ed2eef66633837a5","tid":868084,"uid":87828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"因為發覺真係好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj